data.description:
Price Improvement!  
New roof  11-30-23. New gutters and carport covering to be installed 12/16/23.
New Photos coming soon. 
This Lovely 2,066 sq. ft. brick home sits on a corner lot on the HILL and offers 4 beds, 2 baths 1 car carport.  The extra large gathering room is loaded with a wet/coffee bar with new lighting and mini fridge, custom stained glass windows, custom branded wood mantle ( Previous Owner), whitewashed rock fireplace(gas logs insert available) with bench seating on both sides and storage cabinets below, beautiful built-in bookshelves, matching Wood beams, hidden office nook, NEW mini split heating and air unit, updated breaker box, ADT security system already installed ready for you subscription, and/or Blink security outside camera system ready for you yearly subscription of $100+ there is an abundance of natural lighting from two large Sliding picturesque windows. Kitchen/dining area has custom built-in hutch, breakfast bar with pass-through window, custom chairs, rotating corner cabinet, new dishwasher, new matte black faucet with matching soap dispenser, new electrical outlets, and freshly painted cabinets. Main bedroom has new carpet, built-in storage cabinets, bathroom with a single shower.   Main bathroom has a vanity, recessed lighting and a beautiful mini chandelier.  The backyard has Patio area, an oversized carport, 3 lockable storage rooms, a nice sized storage building. Stove, refrigerator, microwave, and TV mounts will stay.  Schedule your private showing today.
Reserved item, Camera doorbell.
